               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 3ra-92ra)&#xD;
I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah and hymns (fols. 3ra-6vb)&#xD;
I-2) Introductory exhortation (fols. 7ra-8ra)&#xD;
I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki ... "I worship Thee ..." (fol. 8ra-vb)&#xD;
I-4) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 61 miracles (fols. 8vb-92ra)&#xD;
I-5) ʾAkkonu bǝʾǝsi ... "Does not the man ..." (distributed among the miracles of Mary, fols. 13va-48ra), incomplete (31 strophes)&#xD;
II) Taʾāmra Mikāʾel "Miracles of Michael": 3 miracles (fols. 92ra-93rb)&#xD;
III) Taʾāmra Gabra Manfas Qǝddus "Miracles of Gabra Manfas Qǝddus": 1 miracle (fol. 93rb-va)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-4.</summary>
